description: Returns a list of image recipes.

parameters.name: filters
parameters.description: Use the following filters to streamline results: name parentImage platform (dict) --- A filter name and value pair that is used to return a more specific list of results from a list operation. Filters can be used to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as tags, attributes, or IDs. name (string) --- The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. values (list) --- The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. (string) ---

nested_items.name: requestId
nested_items.description: The request ID that uniquely identifies this request.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the image recipe.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the image recipe.

nested_items.name: platform
nested_items.description: The platform of the image recipe.

nested_items.name: owner
nested_items.description: The owner of the image recipe.

nested_items.name: parentImage
nested_items.description: The base image of the image recipe.

nested_items.name: dateCreated
nested_items.description: The date on which this image recipe was created.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.
